trial farming). This isn\u2019t a \\\"narrow\\\" population; it\u2019s a *controlled test* of the hypothesis. Similarly, [HY01-E3]\u2019s antibiotic-IBD link shows that *even in non-farm settings*, early-life microbial disruption (via antibiotics) doubles IBD risk\u2014a finding generalizable to urban populations. These studies collectively demonstrate that *microbial exposure is a critical"}', '2026-02-08 12:13:56.268926');
